---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="账号注销说明 - Compare AI"
  description="Compare AI应用的账号注销流程说明，了解如何删除您的账户和相关数据。"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900 pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <div class="bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-700/50">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-green-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Compare AI
          </span>
          账号注销说明
        </h1>

        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-8 text-center">
            如果您决定不再使用Compare AI服务，可以按照以下步骤注销您的账号
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- 注销流程 -->
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm mr-3">1</span>
                注销流程
              </h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-slate-700/30 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-600/50">
                  <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">步骤一：打开应用菜单</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-300">在Compare AI应用主界面，点击左上角的菜单按钮（三条横线图标）</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-700/30 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-600/50">
                  <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">步骤二：进入用户设置</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-300">在弹出的菜单中，点击您的用户名或头像区域</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-700/30 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-600/50">
                  <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">步骤三：打开用户对话框</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-300">系统将弹出一个包含用户信息和设置选项的对话框</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-700/30 rounded-xl p-6 border border-red-500/50">
                  <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">步骤四：执行注销操作</h3>
                      <p class="text-slate-300">在对话框中找到并点击"注销账号"按钮，确认操作后即可完成注销</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 注销后果 -->
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm mr-3">⚠</span>
                注销后会发生什么
              </h2>
              
              <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-400 mb-4">重要提醒：注销操作不可撤销</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                  一旦确认注销账号，以下数据和功能将被永久删除，且无法恢复：
                </p>
                <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>您的账户信息和个人资料</li>
                  <li>应用内的所有个人设置和偏好</li>
                  <li>收藏的AI模型对比记录</li>
                  <li>自定义的对比配置</li>
                  <li>使用历史和统计数据</li>
                  <li>与账户关联的所有数据和资产</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 注销前的建议 -->
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm mr-3">💡</span>
                注销前的建议
              </h2>
              
              <div class="bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/30 rounded-xl p-6">
                <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                  在执行注销操作之前，我们建议您：
                </p>
                <ul class="text-slate-300 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>备份重要的对比数据或截图保存</li>
                  <li>确认不再需要使用Compare AI服务</li>
                  <li>考虑是否可以通过其他方式解决当前遇到的问题</li>
                  <li>如有疑问，可先联系我们的客服团队</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 替代方案 -->
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm mr-3">🔧</span>
                其他选择
              </h2>
              
              <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                如果您遇到问题或对服务不满意，除了注销账号外，您还可以考虑：
              </p>
              
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-slate-700/30 rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-600/50">
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">暂停使用</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">简单卸载应用，账户数据会保留，随时可以重新安装使用</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-700/30 rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-600/50">
                  <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">联系支持</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">遇到问题可以联系我们的客服团队，我们会尽力帮助解决</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 联系信息 -->
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">需要帮助？</h2>
              <div class="bg-slate-700/30 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-600/50">
                <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                  如果您在注销过程中遇到任何问题，或者对账号注销有疑问，请随时联系我们：
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <p class="text-slate-300">
                    📧 邮箱：<a href="mailto:me@painterner.me" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">me@painterner.me</a>
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-slate-300">
                    📧 邮箱：<a href="mailto:ggwzm2012@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">ggwzm2012@gmail.com</a>
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
                    我们通常会在24小时内回复您的邮件
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-700/50 text-center">
          <a 
            href="/compare-ai" 
            class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>返回Compare AI主页</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
